    {
      "description": "The approved Gradient Specifications table (5 named gradients: Brand Blue→Dark Navy, Sky Blue→Deep Blue, Sunshine→75% Gold, Golden Sand→White→Light Blue, Golden Sand→75% Gold→Sunshine, plus masthead gradient) is not represented as any asset/semantic token set, only individual stop colors exist piecemeal. The guide explicitly states 'never invent gradients,' making the approved list itself a critical catalog entity.",
