      "description": "tok_lisraya_color_gold_cta_variant is keyed as 'color.primary.gold_ffc20e', implying it is part of the PRIMARY palette tier. However #FFC20E is a one-off arrow accent color used only in the Gradient Callout CTA button, distinct from the true primary Gold (#ffc60a). Namespacing it under 'primary' misrepresents its scope and risks confusion with the actual primary Gold token.",
